Two men in a bathhouse. The first has a penis up to the knee, the second has less than average. The second one is interested in:
- How did you enlarge your penis? Share it.
First:
- You take a weight of 100 grams, hang it on it, the next day twice as much and so on until it grows up.
A couple of months later, the same men meet again in the bathhouse, but with the same length of organs. Second:
- Of course, thanks for the advice, I got to seven kilos, after which something cracked and the penis is now not worth it. What do you recommend?
The first one:
- Well, from personal experience... You can keep the flies away, or you can wipe your ass...
